fulltitle: Al Casey chord melody solo on Honeysuckle Rose   GUITAR LESSON
description:
Here is the guitar lesson for Al Casey's amazing chord melody solo on Fats Waller's tune Honeysuckle rose (as played on the video right there: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_5JiD9yxL4U)

Hope you'll like it !
title: Al Casey chord melody solo on Honeysuckle Rose   GUITAR LESSON
